    <div id="about">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title text-center center">
          <h2>About Hotel</h2>
          <hr />
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
            <img
              src="assets/image/bartender.jpg"
              class="img-responsive"
              alt="" />
          </div>
          <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
            <div class="about-text">
              <p>Hotel Paradise</p>
              <p>Good hotel service involves providing attentive, friendly, and efficient service to guests to ensure they have a pleasant and 
                comfortable stay. This can include things like offering timely and accurate information, handling requests and concerns in a prompt 
                and professional manner, and providing a clean and well-maintained environment. Other aspects of good hotel service may include offering 
                a range of amenities and services such as room service, a restaurant, a gym, and a spa, as well as providing helpful recommendations for 
                local attractions and activities. Overall, good hotel service aims to exceed the expectations of guests and make their stay as enjoyable 
                as possible.</p>

              <a href="#package" class="btn btn-default btn-lg page-scroll"
                >Packages</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="featured-hotel" class="fh5co-bg-color">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="section-title text-center center">
            <h2>About Rooms</h2>
            <hr />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="feature-full-1col">
            <div
              class="image"
              style="background-image: url(assets/image/hotel_feture_1.jpg)">
              <div class="descrip text-center">
                <p><small>For as low as</small><span>TK 24,000/night</span></p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="desc">
              <h3>Suite</h3>
              <p>
                A suite is a type of hotel room that is larger and more spacious than 
                a standard room, and often includes additional amenities such as a 
                separate sitting area and a private bedroom. Suite rooms are typically more 
                expensive than standard rooms and are often reserved for special occasions or for 
                travelers who are looking for more luxurious accommodations. Some suite rooms may also 
                come with additional features such as a fireplace, a private balcony, or a kitchenette.

              </p>
              <p>
                <a href="/booking" class="btn btn-primary btn-luxe-primary"
                  >Book Now <i class="ti-angle-right"></i
                ></a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-full-2col">
            <div class="f-hotel">
              <div
                class="image"
                style="background-image: url(assets/image/hotel_feture_2.jpg)">
                <div class="descrip text-center">
                  <p><small>For as low as</small><span>TK 7,000/night</span></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="desc">
                <h3>Standard</h3>
                <p>
                  A standard room is a type of hotel room that is typically the most basic and economical option. 
                  Standard rooms are smaller than suite rooms and may not include additional amenities such as a separate 
                  sitting area or a private bedroom. 

                </p>
                <p>
                  <a href="/booking" class="btn btn-primary btn-luxe-primary"
                    >Book Now <i class="ti-angle-right"></i
                  ></a>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="f-hotel">
              <div
                class="image"
                style="background-image: url(assets/image/hotel_feture_3.jpg)">
                <div class="descrip text-center">
                  <p><small>For as low as</small><span>TK 15,000/night</span></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="desc">
                <h3>Deluxe</h3>
                <p>
                  A deluxe room is a type of hotel room that is typically larger and more luxurious than a standard room. 
                  Deluxe rooms may come with additional amenities and features such as a private balcony, a separate sitting 
                  area, a larger bed, or a more spacious bathroom
                </p>
                <p>
                  <a href="/booking" class="btn btn-primary btn-luxe-primary"
                    >Book Now <i class="ti-angle-right"></i
                  ></a>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
